{"TopicId":194500,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Focus camera on part?","CreatedByName":"ZootinZack","CreatedById":38280,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-06T07:55:53Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ZootinZack","CreatedById":38280,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-06T07:55:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni recently started playing again and I really can swear I remember there was a \u0022focus on part\u0022 function. I can\u0027t find it anymore and it\u0027s making any kind of land docking with robotic parts a real pain.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn short I simply need the camera to focus on one part of a ship, usually a docking port. Or any way I could focus the camera freely around a ship, I\u0027m all ears!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-06-06T08:12:21Z\u0022 title=\u002206/06/2020 08:12  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJune 6, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by ZootinZack\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AHHans","CreatedById":197939,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-06T08:18:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223798205\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591430153\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002238280\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ZootinZack\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, ZootinZack said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni recently started playing again and I really can swear I remember there was a \u0022focus on part\u0022 function.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is still there. To Access it you need to access the Part Action Window (\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Part Action Window\u0022\u003EPAW\u003C/abbr\u003E) of the part by right-clicking on the part. In that window there is an option to \u0022Aim Camera\u0022 to this part. E.g. here:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 style=\u0022width:800px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 alt=\u0022s4E9PHj.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/s4E9PHj.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-06T09:52:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou may need to turn on the \u0022Enable Advanced Tweakables\u0022 in the Settings in order to have that option in the menu.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AHHans","CreatedById":197939,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-06T09:58:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223798227\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591437139\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou may need to turn on the \u0022Enable Advanced Tweakables\u0022 in the Settings in order to have that option in the menu.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh *bleep*! Yes, that could be. Why aren\u0027t they on by default? Or at least switch on as soon as you register for a Forum account?\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S. And while you are at it: also switch on the \u0022Extended Burn Indicator\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZootinZack","CreatedById":38280,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-06T16:39:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223798228\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591437492\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197939\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AHHans\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, AHHans said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh *bleep*! Yes, that could be. Why aren\u0027t they on by default? Or at least switch on as soon as you register for a Forum account?\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S. And while you are at it: also switch on the \u0022Extended Burn Indicator\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAaaaah mf thanks a lot this might be it. I was really raging!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZootinZack","CreatedById":38280,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-07T06:15:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223798227\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194500\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591437139\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou may need to turn on the \u0022Enable Advanced Tweakables\u0022 in the Settings in order to have that option in the menu.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust played and that\u0027s what it was. Thanks a lot!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}